  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of study is to determine the effect of hyaluronic acid on the formation of
      post-operative adhesions. It will be a randomized control trial comparing the product against
      normal saline.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
